setup.py: change setup_requires to tests_require

setup.py: change setup_requires to tests_require

Merge pull request #4 from denis-sumin/feature/ignore-none

Add ignore_none for dict_to_protobuf

Add ignore_none for dict_to_protobuf

This option enables creating of protobuf objects from dicts, in which
some values are None. Such value is treated as absence
of the appropriate key.

Merge pull request #5 from denis-sumin/feature/including_default_value_fields

Add including_default_value_fields for protobuf_to_dict

Add including_default_value_fields for protobuf_to_dict

This option has the same behavior as google.protobuf.json_format.MessageToJson:
if a singular primitive field has no value, it is filled with a default value.
